00:19:23.980 --> 00:19:27.452
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:20:03.660 --> 00:20:05.230
[END PLAYBACK]

00:20:05.230 --> 00:20:06.554
[APPLAUSE]

00:20:06.554 --> 00:20:07.804
SPEAKER 1: That was excellent.

00:20:10.590 --> 00:20:14.850
That dance performance brought
to life the frustrations

00:20:14.850 --> 00:20:15.560
of the character.

00:20:15.560 --> 00:20:16.380
[LAUGHTER]

